echo "ðŸš€ Báº¯t Ä‘áº§u cÃ i Ä‘áº·t Pannel Server CentOS 7..."
echo " LÆ°u Ã PhiÃªn Báº£n NÃ y DÃ nh Cho CentOS 7/8 : Rocky/Alma linux 7/8 "
echo " Náº¿u Ai CÃ i TrÃªn VMware/VirtualBox ThÃ¬ HÃ£y XoÃ¡ VÃ  Táº£i Láº¡i Repo Äá»ƒ TrÃ¡nh Lá»—i "
echo " Nhá»› CÃ i CÃ¡i Fix Repo NÃ y TrÆ°á»›c Khi Cháº¡y Scipt BÃªn DÆ°á»›i "
echo " link :https://www.mediafire.com/file/i6070ayons3b9gy/Fix_EROR_Repo.txt/file"
